title: Cap crown
description: Cap crown of Brussels bobbin lace with a design of a fountain surmounted by chinoiserie pavilion and flanked by floral and foliated sprays and rocaille decoration. Fond: droschel. Modes: fond de neige, enchainettes and portes.
